Analysis of Data Carpentrys Archived Survey Data

Contributors: Kari L. Jordan and Paula Andrea Work Cycle: Ganymede

In August 2017 Data Carpentry launched new pre- and post-workshop surveys that included skills-based questions. This report is an analysis of the old pre- and post-workshop surveys.

Responses collected for Data Carpentrys workshops from XX through XX are included in this report. In this XX year period, nearly XX responses were collected.

PDFs of both the pre and post workshop surveys, the data used in this analysis, and full R code are located in the data-carpentry-projects folder in the Carpentries assessment-projects repo on GitHub.

Community members are invited to contribute code to this analysis. Feel free to use the data and tell us about your findings.
